            <span class="utterance" who="#gertnerA" start="5180.898" end="x"> ...these carts. And this was the worst, dragging these carts. We couldn't drag. We were weak. Drag them up hills on the road. And they beat. The cart detail always remained behind.</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#boderD" start="5191.271" end="x">Hm.</span>
