                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">Alexander Gertner</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#gertnerA" start="5192.025" end="x">The others walked on foot. It was easier for them to walk. The others were always rotated. Here came the <a class="term" href="#vothG_lager">lager</a>
                        <a class="term" href="#vothG_commandant">commandant</a> to the back. But the <a class="term" href="#vothG_lager">lager</a> elder did not like it. If he saw that the cart drags behind and the others already are in front, he began to beat with the cudgel so that...beat to death. I was also once at the cart. I was always on the cart detail. I was mostly on the cart detail, because they saw such a tall man, so they thought that he was strong.</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
