            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#gertnerA" start="5219.593" end="x">At night I used to drag myself away. Since I was not seen, I used to drag myself away, used to run to the front, so as not to be on the cart detail. Once there behind...by the carts when we had stopped a little, the <a class="term" href="#vothG_ss">SS</a> were eating. We were not given anything, but they were eating the dinner there. So one <a class="term" href="#vothG_ss">SS</a> man threw down the bread rinds, the burnt [crusts] of the bread. He threw it away.</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
