            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#gertnerA" start="5240.782" end="x">So we went to pick them up. We were so hungry. There was one...I saw others were picking them up, so I also ran to pick them up. And there was a <a class="term" href="#vothG_lager">lager</a>-...still from <a class="placename" href="#vothC123" type="camp">Bolkenhain</a>, a <a class="term" href="#vothG_lager">lager</a> elder, a...a <a class="term" href="#vothG_block">block</a> leader, a Jew. He was still mad at me. He says, 'I am going to tell on you to the <a class="term" href="#vothG_lager">lager</a>-...to the <a class="term" href="#vothG_lager">lager</a> elder. You were taking bread.' The <a class="term" href="#vothG_lager">lager</a> elder comes over, so he says, 'He took bread from the sentries.' He says, 'Yes?' And he begins cudgeling me. He beat me so that I was so blue, blue all over, swollen all over [?]. </span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
