            <span class="who">
                <span class="">Alexander Gertner</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="#gertnerA" start="6485.428" end="x">And then all the others, the other hundred and fifty above the three hundred, these were sent to France. They already are all in Palestine. [This, of course, is not entirely correct. By 1946 many of them were still in the shelterhouses of France.--DPB.]</span>
